data.description: Discover your new home in Sugar Hill with this spacious 4-bed, 2.5-bath gem perfectly situated on a level cul-de-sac lot and adjoins wide open green space perfect for outdoor activities! Nestled in a prime location, it offers privacy with a fenced-in yard and a 2-car garage. Inside, you'll discover a soaring 2 story foyer that leads to an open concept layout for easy entertaining, and features formal living and dining rooms, an open kitchen with island seating and breakfast area, family room, and laundry room. The owners' suite boasts a cozy sitting area, his/hers closets and en-suite bath with separate vanities, soaking tub and a shower. The back has a special feature addition that could be used as an art/yoga studio, workshop or exercise room. The roof is only 5 years old. Conveniently located minutes away from Lake Lanier, parks, shopping, and downtown Sugar Hill. This home sits in an Award-Winning School District promising an ideal living space.
